Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}國會讓美國失望{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're almost a month into the strike,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}罷工已近一個月{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}數百萬的孩子  困在家裏無法上課{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and we've got millions of kids  stuck home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你怪罪白宮或國會嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you blame the White House or Congress?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.39,0:00:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我個人不同情教師{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I personally have very little sympathy  for the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}國會讓教師失望{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're over three weeks into this strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}罷工已三周{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}耗損全國數十億美元{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's costing the country billions of dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 未找出解決之道…  - 表明立場{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-and instead of offering solutions...  -There's a big difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}和坐視不理差很多{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}taking a stand and sitting on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}工會流乾稅賦！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不知道要叫懦弱…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't know whether to call it cowardice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是他的議程{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's his agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}教師應教書…  回家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}問題是他剽竊合理的傳統理想{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And the problem is that he stole  sound, conservative ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他做的明智之舉  就是抄襲共和黨政綱{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The only smart thing he's done is lift  his platform from the Republican platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我承認，琳達  這出乎我意料之外{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I admit it, Linda. This got away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我們無法讓時光倒流  我們得堅持立場{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But we can't turn back time.  We have to hold our ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不管我們的支持率繼續下滑？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}While our approval ratings  continue to nosedive?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}多年來史皮奈拉和我合作  數十件勞工提案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Spinella and I worked together for years  on dozens of labor-related bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我以為他會很理性  - 你錯了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I thought he'd be reasonable.  -Well, you were wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒料到他會瘋到展開罷工{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I didn't think he'd be  insane enough to go on strike,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也沒料到罷工會持續這麼久{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I didn't think the strike  would last this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你錯估這事件兩次{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So you've been wrong twice about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我怎能相信堅持立場是對的？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Why should I believe  you're right about holding out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們威脅勞資談判是為了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We threatened collective  bargaining in order to get
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}成績標準和特許補助{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}performance standards and charter funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那是我們談好的立場{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's the deal that we made.  We took that stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在若讓步，就全盤皆輸{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We lay down now, we lose it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:00:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有改革，只有空洞的提案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There'll be no reform, just an empty bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我瞭解這個邏輯，法蘭  但現在得做損害控制{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I understand the logic, Frank,  but we're in damage control now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我們無法止這個血  卻弄出另一個傷口{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But we can't close one wound  by opening another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們是民主黨{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But we're the Democrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們該為教師喉舌{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're the ones who are supposed  to be defending the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}魚與熊掌無法兼得，琳達{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But you can't have it both ways, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}無法達到改革{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You can't have the reform you want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}又滿足教師{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and keep the teachers happy  at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}從一開始你就知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You knew that when we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好吧，若讓我們選擇  我們該滿足教師{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay, then if we have to choose,  we choose to keep the teachers happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那就大錯特錯，琳達  我們已無法回頭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That is a mistake, Linda.  We've already crossed the Rubicon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我跟你說，總統希望改變提案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm telling you this.  The President wants to change the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}三周前就該這麼做{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We should've done it three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們當時沒做  所以現在你得照做{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We didn't. So you have to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}琳達，請再給我多點時間{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Give me more time, Linda, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果我能停止罷工  保留我們要的提案內容{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I can break this strike and get  everything we want in this bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這不是比讓步更好嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}can we agree that's preferable to folding?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果能辦到…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Of course. If we can count on that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那就相信我，再給我一周{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Then count on me for just one more week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}若到時罷工還沒停止  我就修改提案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If the strike isn't over by then,  I'll change the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 法蘭…  - 再一周就好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Frank...  -No. One more week. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}真是再糟也不過了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is the worst possible position to be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果我修改提案  總統還是會覺得我失敗{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I water down the bill,  the President will still see me as a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果罷工一周內沒結束  我就窮途末路{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If the strike doesn't end in a week,  I've forced myself into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只有全面勝利  才能讓我重獲他的青睞{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Only total victory will put me  back in his good graces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}否則就是出局{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The alternative is exile,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}之前五個月就是白忙一場{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}which would mean  the last five months were for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不能跌回原點{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I cannot abide falling back to square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}夫人，議員找我嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Does the Congressman need me, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不，我只是想邀你喝杯咖啡{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. I just was wondering  if you wanted a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我剛煮了一壺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I just brewed a fresh pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 夫人，不用了，謝謝  - 確定？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I'm good, ma'am. But thanks.  -Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我再幾個小時就下班了，沒事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My shift's done in a couple hours. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}來吧，放鬆一下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know, come on. Stretch your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我可不接受拒絕{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I won't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你當議員保鑣前做什麼工作？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What did you do before you  joined the leadership detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我在華府當警察{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was a cop here in D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在那之前  我在海軍陸戰隊服役，夫人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Before that, I was in the Marines, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 謝謝  - 你有在國外服役嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Thank you.  -Did you serve overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有的，夫人，巴林  之後去阿富汗{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I did, ma'am. Bahrain, then Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}第二次派駐海外  主要是在可蘭山谷{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Served most of my second tour  in the Korengal Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你想知道我是否殺過人？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You wanna know if I killed anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想我知道答案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think I know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我約了柏許晚餐，我要…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I got a dinner meeting with Birch. I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我邀他來喝咖啡{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I invited him in for coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}喝快點，要出發了…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, drink it fast. We leave in five...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}趴下！遠離窗戶！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Get down! Stay away from the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}停下！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我會安排六名優秀手下  24小時保護你們{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You'll have six of my best men  covering you around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那你之前為什麼沒安排{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I guess I'm wondering why  we didn't at least have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}其中一個優秀手下保護我們{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}one of your best men covering us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他會被懲戒的，議員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He'll be disciplined, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他在住宅區開槍{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He shot a gun in a residential neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 開除他  - 我們會仔細調查{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I want him fired.  -There will be a full investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}採取必要措施{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and we'll take the necessary action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}史提夫絕不會讓這種事發生{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Steve never would've let this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他好點了嗎？  有他在，我會覺得安全多了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is he better yet? Because I would  feel a lot safer if he was with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}遺憾的是  他不會再回來了，議員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Unfortunately, he won't be coming back, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我以為他只是膽囊感染{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I thought he just had a gallbladder infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒錯，但不只這些{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He did, they found more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他得了胰腺癌末期{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}His pancreas, stage four.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 老天  - 天啊，這麼嚴重{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Jesus.  -Oh, my God. That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他還能活多久？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How much longer does he have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不長，幾周{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not long. A few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}至少他老婆是這麼告訴我的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}At least that's what his wife told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們必須去看他  你能查出他在哪嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We have to go see him.  Can you get the information where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當然，我會馬上告知{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Of course.  I'll make sure you get it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 謝謝，隊長  - 謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Thank you, Captain.  -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不客氣，晚安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're welcome. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 前門  - 是的，長官{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Front door.  -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的佩槍{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還有你的徽章{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your badge, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}長官，要我停職？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Am I suspended, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}嫌犯徒步逃跑  你居然對他開槍？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You had a suspect on foot,  and you fire your gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 長官，我知道…  - 知道我多有丟人嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Sir, I realize that...  -Do you know how this reflects on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我的手下居然如此魯莽？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That one of our men could be so careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不只擅離職守去喝咖啡{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not only do you abandon  your post for coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還有可能射傷路人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You could've killed a bystander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那顆子彈是在某家前廊找到的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That slug was found  on somebody's front stoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}要是射進他們家呢？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What if it went in their house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的徽章，米契{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your badge, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}兩個原因，其實都一樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Two reasons,  which are really the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我受夠了為別人工作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was sick of working for other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道我比我的老闆還能幹{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I knew I could do a better job  than my bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們不斷壓迫、排斥我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They kept trying to suppress me,  shutting me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}於是我說：  「我自己來」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So I said, "Fuck it. I'll do it my way."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 然後你就辭職了？  - 和你不一樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-And then you just quit?  -Not like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我拚死拚活工作  才存夠錢開《頭條報導》{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I slaved away until I lined up  the money to start Slugline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}《頭條報導》茁壯之後  你打算如何？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Once Slugline gets big enough,  what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}像亞莉安娜一樣賣了公司？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are you gonna sell it like Arianna?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}可能吧，之後誰知道？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Probably. And then who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}迎接任何挑戰，或許去上海吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Whatever the next adventure is.  Maybe Shanghai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以我可能沒辦法做兩年？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So I shouldn't expect  to have a job in two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你會想兩年  都做同一份工作嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you ever wanna have any job  for more than two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你呢？你有什麼雄心壯志？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What about you? What's your big plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我還不知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}拜託，  《頭條報導》  只是你的踏腳板{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Come on.  Slugline is just a stepping stone for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我得接個電話  - 去忙吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-You know what? I should take this.  -Go. Do your thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你有證據  證明是史皮奈拉做的嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hey. Do you have proof  Spinella was behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}寫下來  全國教師罷工第三周後…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Put it in context.  Three weeks into a national teachers' strike...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}提案負責人  法蘭斯安德沃的私宅…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}At the home of Francis Underwood,  who has led the charge on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就是這樣，趕快發文  免得我鄰居通知地方晚間新聞{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There you go. Now post that before one of  my neighbors calls a local 11:00 hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我何時再見你？  - 我是受害人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-When do I see you next?  -I'm background on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 不是你的線人  - 現在不方便？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I'm not your source.  -You can't talk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 對  - 何時？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-No.  -When?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很快，迫不及待{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Soon, with bells on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「多些書，少些磚塊」如何？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What about  "more school books, less bricks"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}太廣泛了  我們要更一針見血{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, it's too broad.  We need a better sound bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}更精準、更能將矛頭  指向史皮奈拉的話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Something specific, something that  points the finger directly at Spinella.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他會否認涉案  - 當然了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-He'll deny any involvement.  -Well, of course he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 要怎麼辦？  - 就說他管不好手下的人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-So how do we get around that?  -We say he can't control his troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 沒有證據是教師做的  - 還會是誰？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-There's no evidence it was a teacher.  -Who else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他會將罷工怪在國會頭上{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Look, he's gonna shift blame for  the strike back on Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們要更明確、清新的標語{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. We need something clear,  something clean,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}聽了就忘不了的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}something that sticks in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「教師得學會自製」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"Teachers need a lesson in self-restraint."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你沒聽懂我的意思  大家都愛戴教師{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. You're not hearing me.  People like teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們要能讓史皮奈拉  變成壞人的標語{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. We need something  that makes Spinella the villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他無控制力，無法…  - 失序勞工{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-His lack of control, his inability...  -Disorganized labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}失序勞工，直接簡單{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's disorganized labor, plain and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}教師罷工轉向暴力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}憤怒的教師  朝議員住宅窗戶扔磚塊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When you've got angry teachers throwing  bricks through congressmen's windows,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那是工會領袖的責任{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}you've gotta blame the union leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們會為高階議員增加保安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We'll be beefing up the security  for the entire leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我強烈建議馬帝史皮奈拉  管好他的人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I strongly encourage Marty Spinella  to keep his people in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這變得像是失序勞工了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is starting to look like  disorganized labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你真的認為  是馬帝史皮奈拉的錯？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you really think  Marty Spinella is to blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不論史皮奈拉先生  是否是幕後主使{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Whether Mr. Spinella is behind this or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他都該注意言詞{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}he might wanna tone down the rhetoric,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}以免失序勞工變成組織犯罪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}before disorganized labor  turns into organized crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒人能證明這點  這就是最有力的回應{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No one can prove anything.  So that's the most cogent response.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那就上電視說明  你譴責一切形式的暴力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, go on TV and say that.  You deplore violence in any form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}該負責任的是國會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's Congress that should take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不想自貶到法蘭的水平{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't want to degenerate to Frank's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們得結束磚塊事件  這分散大家對議題的注意力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We need to kill this brick thing.  It's distracting people from the issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 說得對  - 熱度過了，就會消失{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-She's right.  -lt'll eat up one cycle, and it'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不，這個故事越來越引人關注{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. This story is getting traction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 罷工支持率在下降  - 總統支持率也是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Support for the strike is dipping.  -So is the President's approval ratings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但不管如何，他還能執政三年{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But he gets to stay in the Oval Office  another three years, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}再拖三周我們可承受不了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can't afford another three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我叫工會罷工時  就說過要準備好長期抗戰{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When I told the unions to strike,  I told them to prepare for the long haul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就算他們沒錢了  我們還是繼續罷工{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All right? Their accounts dry up,  we keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們會想出方法  我絕不會對這種事讓步{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We figure it out. I am not going  to blink over something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好，但要是輸了這場公關戰{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Fine. But ifwe lose  the public relations battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}堅持可毫無好處{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}none of that does us any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭要我們採取防守{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank wants us on the defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這件事會平息的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think this story is going to blow over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果我錯了，我們會重新評估{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I'm wrong, we'll reevaluate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我想再堅持一、兩天  好嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I wanna give it  another day or two first. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}亞當{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hi, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你還好嗎？我看到新聞了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You all right? I saw the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我沒事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一定把你嚇壞了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's gotta rattle the nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}磚頭居然破窗而入{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Brick coming through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}的確有點{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It did, some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你還住在家裏嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So are you staying in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在有加派保安人員，所以…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We've got extra security now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我擔心你，所以想問候你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, it made me think of you,  so I figured I'd just check in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}真是謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們還沒談呢？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We still haven't talked, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 沒必要  - 我覺得有必要{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-There's no need to.  -I think we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我是這麼想的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Here's how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你要我過去，我去了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You asked me to come down. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們都理解那代表的意義{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We both had ideas  about what that could mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}或許相差無幾{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Probably very similar ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但之後你改變主意{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But then you changed your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那就這樣吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們還是可以連絡  或繼續當朋友{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There's no reason we can't be in touch  or remain friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}別自欺欺人了，亞當{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let's not fool ourselves, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不會再打電話給你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So I won't call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 結束了  - 這不是我的意思{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Done.  -I'm not saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那你的意思是？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我只是關心你才打電話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I just called because I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒別的意思{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你想再談，就打電話給我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you wanna talk again, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}若不想，我瞭解，隨你決定{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If not, I understand. It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你覺得我無理取鬧？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You think I'm being unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我覺得你是做你該做的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think you're doing  whatever it is you need to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不會質疑這點{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I'm not gonna question it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你打電話來真好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It was sweet of you to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你大概得繼續工作了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Listen, you probably  need to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我得繼續工作，該掛電話了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know I do. I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 保重  - 好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Take care.  -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 法蘭，有時間嗎？  - 裏面見{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Frank, you got a minute?  -I'll see you inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想當州長，希望你能幫忙{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wanna be governor, and I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我還在人選名單上嗎？  - 是的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Am I still on the short list?  -You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我一個多月滴酒不沾  我戒酒了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I haven't had a drink  in over a month. I'm clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是因為我要求你戒酒  還是你想戒酒？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is that because I asked,  or because it's what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}該是我對自己負責的時候{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It was about time I took  responsibility for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}負責是一回事，值得欽佩{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Taking responsibility is one thing,  and it's admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是競選大州的州長  就另當別論了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But running for governor of a major  state is a whole nother ball game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，我跟你說，我入選國會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let me tell you something, Frank.  I got elected to Congress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那是因為我抓住機會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}'cause I seized the moment  that opportunity struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你把我留在名單上  我想抓住那機會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You kept me on that list.  I wanna seize that opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你幫我的忙  我會為你付出一切{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you help me out,  I'll give you everything I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我就在等你這句話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, that's all I've been waiting to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好吧，我跟你說{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All right. I'll tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我得打幾通電話  和一些人談談{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need to make some calls,  check in with some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}給我幾天，我再回覆{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Give me a few days. I'll get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 當然  - 還有，彼得…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Of course.  -And, Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我總算看到真正的你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I feel like I've met the real you  for the first time just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}珍妮{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 不方便嗎？  - 不會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-ls this a bad time?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一點也不會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}抱歉，我不知道你會來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm sorry. I didn't know you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}坐我的椅子吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Here. Take my chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 不用，沒事  - 我來拿花{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-No. I'm fine.  -I'll take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你好，史提夫  - 你好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Hello, Steve.  -Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}花需要加點水，我馬上回來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}These could use some water.  I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭斯和我知道時很難過{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Francis and I were so upset when we heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}抱歉我沒能早點來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm sorry I haven't come sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不想要太多人知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I didn't want too many people knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我明白{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭斯很想過來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Francis wishes he could be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他希望你知道他為你禱告{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He wants you to know he's praying for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}來不成？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Couldn't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒辦法  現在有大規模的教師罷工{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, there's a big teachers' strike  going on right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他困在辦公室好幾周了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and he's been stuck in his office for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我懂，我有看到新聞{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I get it. I saw the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 磚頭  - 對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-The brick.  -Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我跟法蘭斯說  若你在場，可能就不會發生了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I told Francis that probably wouldn't  have happened if you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}可能不會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我從未見過他禱告{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I never seen him pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這八年都沒見過{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not in eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你說他為我禱告{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You said he was praying for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你看過我們上教堂{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You've seen us in church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對，但是我從未進到教堂裏面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, but I never went inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這些花真美{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They're just gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}安德沃夫人，謝謝你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Mrs. Underwood, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}叫我克萊兒就好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Please, call me Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我知道你還有事要忙  - 是的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I know you got things to do.  -Of course.
