Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.61,0:24:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有什麼比一張白紙更好？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What's better than a blank slate  in the right hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.84,0:24:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}愛德，快走吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Ed, you need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.11,0:24:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員，你有時間嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Congressman, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.18,0:24:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝你，派翠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you, Patti.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.25,0:24:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 叫他打電話給我  - 好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Have him call me.  -I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.95,0:24:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}愛德？拜託{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Ed? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.12,0:24:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 什麼事？  - 我來處理{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-What is going on?  -I'm taking care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.59,0:24:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員，一會兒就好，拜託{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}One second, sir. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.59,0:24:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好吧，快點，米契{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All right. Make it fast, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.56,0:24:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我難以啟齒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's not easy for me to ask this,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.69,0:24:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我在想你能不能  跟我老闆說點好話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but I was wondering if you could  put in a good word with my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.23,0:24:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好話？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}A good word?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們要開除我，議員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They're going to discharge me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.37,0:24:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很清楚我搞砸了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I messed up. I'm fully aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.37,0:24:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我的工作對我很重要{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But my job, it means everything to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.41,0:24:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道你說一句好話就能…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I know a good word from you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.64,0:24:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我對你個人沒有意見，米契{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Look, I have nothing  against you personally, Meechum,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.48,0:24:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我不能干涉這類事情{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but I can't get involved  in these sort of affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.61,0:24:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}規定就是規定{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There's protocols and rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.01,0:24:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員，請你和卡帝夫…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sir, please, if you spoke to Cardiff...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我無能為力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There is nothing that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.85,0:25:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只有你能說服隊長了，議員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If anyone could convince the Captain,  it would be you, Congressman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.65,0:25:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}抱歉，祝你好運，米契{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm sorry. I wish you all the best, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.69,0:25:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}道格{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.50,0:25:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}邦尼霍爾說了什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What did Barney Hull say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.90,0:25:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們會是第一個知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That we'd be the first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.43,0:25:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不敢相信  到現在還沒有報警電話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I can't believe there hasn't been  a single 911 call.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.00,0:25:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是有很多  但不是我們要的那種{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There's been plenty.  It's just not the sort we're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.51,0:25:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}亞特蘭大的孩子{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We got that kid in Atlanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.61,0:25:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不行，得要是這裏的  我不能去搭飛機{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, it's got to be here.  I can't be getting on a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.94,0:25:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}看起來太取巧了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It looks too opportunistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.34,0:25:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}或許該擴大範圍？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Maybe if we open it up a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.61,0:25:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們不能降低水準{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, we cannot lower our standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.38,0:25:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}再耐心等等{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We just have to be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.22,0:25:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}新規則，既然辯論結束了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}New rule. Now that the debate's over,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.82,0:25:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭安德沃  得告訴我們究竟怎麼回事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank Underwood has to tell us  what the hell that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.95,0:25:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}母音運動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.05,0:25:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}說真的，議員，那是開玩笑嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Seriously, Congressman, was that a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.22,0:25:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我好久沒看過這種事…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I haven't seen something  just lay there like that since...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.36,0:25:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}得回溯到我的高中舞會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I gotta go all the way back to my prom night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.77,0:25:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}拜託解決這場罷工{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Can we just settle this strike please?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.94,0:25:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}教師離開教室很久了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Teachers have been out  of the classroom for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.94,0:25:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}中學生開始偷嘗禁果{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}middle-schoolers are starting to  have sex with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.24,0:26:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}夠了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.81,0:26:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不懂你為什麼要看{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't know why you had it on  in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.82,0:26:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我愛你，法蘭斯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I love you, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.55,0:26:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.72,0:26:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們該多對彼此說這句話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We should say that more often to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.53,0:26:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我得清理思緒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need to clear my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.30,0:26:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}…在機場北邊與東邊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}...north and east of the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.30,0:27:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}開會前幫我弄好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm gonna need that in time for that meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.50,0:27:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得，我們談談吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Peter, let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.91,0:27:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我和派翠西亞惠特克談過  她同意了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So. I've spoken to Patricia Whittaker.  She's on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.95,0:27:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你會得到民主黨全委會  四百萬啟動補助{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You'll be getting $4 million  in start-up funding from the DNC.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.19,0:27:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我來挑選團隊，你八月宣佈{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll pick the team. You announce in August.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.32,0:27:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是選戰今天就展開{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But the campaign starts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.29,0:27:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你做好準備了嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.76,0:27:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我已經擬好一份政綱{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I've already put together a platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.43,0:27:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還是泛泛之論  但我們可以多加琢磨{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's mostly broad strokes, but we can hone it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.43,0:27:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很好，我們的首要任務  就是你戒酒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Good. The first thing we need to address  is your sobriety.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.97,0:27:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不用擔心{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.23,0:27:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你有參加聚會嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Have you been going to meetings?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.47,0:27:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你是說戒酒會？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You mean AA?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.97,0:27:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 對  - 我不喜歡這檔子事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Yes.  -That's not really my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.84,0:27:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你要我幫忙{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you want my help,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.98,0:27:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那參加聚會是我的要求{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}then going to meetings  is my one requirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.11,0:27:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道我有酗酒問題，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know I had a problem, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.08,0:27:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我承認{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.72,0:27:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我對此負責{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I've taken responsibility for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.32,0:27:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是沒必要去參加聚會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but I don't think going to  meetings is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.42,0:27:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你在恢復期  不能靠意志力撐下去，彼得{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You cannot white-knuckle  your recovery, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.26,0:27:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這場競選會是  你一生做過最艱困的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This campaign will be the hardest thing  you've ever done in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.26,0:27:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我明白，我準備好了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I realize that. I'm prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.60,0:28:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你認為你準備好了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.30,0:28:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我們經不起任何風險{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But we can't take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.30,0:28:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}黨部對你寄予厚望{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The party's investing in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.63,0:28:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我必須確保你全力以赴{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need to make sure  you're investing in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.11,0:28:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好吧，我會盡力而為{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All right. I'll do whatever I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.74,0:28:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很好，明早開始{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Good. You'll start tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.01,0:28:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 道格會帶你去  - 史坦普？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Doug will take you.  -Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.48,0:28:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他戒酒14年了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's been sober 14 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.05,0:28:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}道格有酗酒問題？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Doug has a drinking problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.45,0:28:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}曾經，現在沒了  他會當你的保證人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Had. Not anymore. He'll be your sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.09,0:28:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}同時，我要你  去見我的老婆，克萊兒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}In the meantime, I want you  to meet with my wife, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.06,0:28:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她推動淨水創權{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She runs the Clean Water lnitiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.56,0:28:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她等著見你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She's expecting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.63,0:28:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以空出你的行程  現在就去那裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}so clear your schedule  and head over there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.03,0:28:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.93,0:28:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.33,0:28:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝你相信我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}For believing in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.64,0:28:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你會是絕佳候選人，彼得{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're gonna make a great candidate, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.98,0:28:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}造船廠關閉空出  一千一百英畝的聯邦土地{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The shipyard closing  frees up 1,100 acres of federal land.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.05,0:28:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們的目的是  通過德拉瓦河分水嶺法案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Our goal is to pass a Watershed Act  for the Delaware River.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.72,0:28:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們用環保方式開發土地{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We develop the land in an  environmentally responsible way,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.49,0:29:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}同時創造工作機會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}creating jobs in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.12,0:29:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 多少工作？  - 數以千計{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-How many jobs?  -Thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.79,0:29:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}目標收益兩億{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're aiming for the $200 million mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.83,0:29:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們有一堆事要做{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We got a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.16,0:29:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒錯，但你能從議員著手{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We do, but you can start  with the congressmen
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.80,0:29:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}找出落在分水嶺內的選區{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}whose districts fall within the watershed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.00,0:29:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你能給看我草案嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you have a draft of the bill  you can show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.50,0:29:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們從未發起環境立法{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We haven't sponsored  any environmental legislation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.94,0:29:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我是史提夫，別回電  煩請造訪…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.57,0:29:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們會和你的手下  討論草案內容{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We'll draft it in consultation with your staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.81,0:29:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}吉莉安是這邊的主要負責人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Gillian will be the point person on our end.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.58,0:29:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我沒有立法經驗{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't have any legislation experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.45,0:29:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我會幫你  - 何時開始？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I'll help you.  -When do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.71,0:29:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}已經開始了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.12,0:29:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}介紹他給研究小組{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Will you introduce him to the research team?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.28,0:29:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我等會就過去  - 好的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I'll be there in one second.  -Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.62,0:29:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}明天可以嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.06,0:29:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}總統先生？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.56,0:29:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}結束這一切{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I want it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.16,0:29:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 越快越好  - 修改提案，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-As soon as possible.  -Gut the bill, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.13,0:29:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}採取必要措施結束罷工{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do whatever's necessary to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.63,0:29:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}總統先生，如果現在屈服{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Mr. President, if we give in now,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.20,0:29:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}大眾不會覺得你贏得勝利{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}the public won't credit you with a victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.87,0:29:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}連邊都沾不上  他們會說我們節節敗退{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not even a hollow one.  They'll chalk it up as a colossal defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.27,0:29:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那是你的過失，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, that's on you, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.04,0:29:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你讓局勢演變得一發不可收拾{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You let this situation devolve to where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.54,0:29:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}美國史上最大規模教師罷工  使我備受指摘{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I've already been blamed  for the largest teachers' strike in U.S. history.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.61,0:30:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不會為歹戲拖棚負責{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I won't be held accountable  for it dragging on months and months.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.98,0:30:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}總統先生  我們要用你的關係結束罷工{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Mr. President, we have to  end this strike on your terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.75,0:30:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 不能用別人的  - 怎麼做？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Not anyone else's.  -How?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.09,0:30:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}和馬帝史皮奈拉在CNN辯論？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}By debating Marty Spinella on CNN?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.56,0:30:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}總統，你一向對我信任有加{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sir, you have placed your faith in me thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.03,0:30:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我懇求你繼續信任我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I would ask that you continue to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.10,0:30:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的做法毫無效用，法蘭  所以我要介入{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, whatever you're doing, Frank,  isn't working, so I'm stepping in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.00,0:30:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}照琳達說的，修改提案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Gut the bill. Like Linda said.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.77,0:30:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.87,0:30:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}抱歉，總統先生，我辦不到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm sorry, Mr. President, but I will not do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.35,0:30:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你讓驕傲沖昏腦袋了，法蘭？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are you letting pride  cloud your judgment, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.15,0:30:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}恕我直言，總統  是你讓恐懼沖昏你的腦袋{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Respectfully, sir,  you're allowing fear to cloud yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.39,0:30:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對自由世界最有權勢的人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not an easy thing, to say no
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.89,0:30:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}說不並不容易{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}to the most powerful man in the free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.19,0:30:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但有時唯一  能贏取上級尊重的方法{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But sometimes the only way  to gain your superior's respect
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.13,0:30:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就是違抗{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}is to defy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.70,0:30:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}琳達，今天行程是？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What do we have on the schedule, Linda?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.07,0:30:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你要和聯邦監督委員會開會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your meeting with the  Fed Oversight Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.04,0:30:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝，總統先生{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.10,0:30:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你有我的簡報？  - 這裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Do you have my briefing?  -Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.64,0:30:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很好，我們看一遍{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Good. Let's look it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.17,0:31:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}掃瞄代碼- 地圖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.91,0:31:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你好，和彼得談得如何？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hi. How'd it go with Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.38,0:31:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很順利{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.18,0:31:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他投入嗎？  - 非常投入{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-ls he game?  -Completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.62,0:31:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.78,0:31:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我如釋重負{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's a big weight off my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.39,0:31:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你聽起來很疲憊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You sound tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.62,0:31:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}疲憊、不耐煩{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tired. Impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.96,0:31:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我能幫什麼忙？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.59,0:31:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不用了，這只能聽天由命{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Nothing. This one's up to fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.63,0:31:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不喜歡聽天由命{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't like when we leave things to fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.96,0:31:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我也不喜歡{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.33,0:31:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是說我今晚得獨守空閨？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Does that mean I'm gonna have  the bed to myself tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.20,0:31:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}可能吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.14,0:31:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}道格不能頂替你嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Can't Doug man the fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.21,0:31:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他可以，但是我會輾轉難眠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, he could, but I'd just toss and turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.67,0:31:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}既然睡不著  乾脆在這裏熬夜好了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I'm not gonna sleep,  I might as well not sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.14,0:31:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好吧，我會開著手機{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I'll leave the ringer on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.35,0:31:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}想要人陪伴就打電話給我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Call me if you want company.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.48,0:31:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好，晚安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I will. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.35,0:31:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}晚安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.86,0:31:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你應該回家  我可以處理剩下的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You should go home.  I could take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.89,0:31:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謹慎，這有益無害{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Vigilance. It's good for the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.76,0:31:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}安檢，16街和Q街轉角{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}10-59. Corner of 16th and Q. 10-59.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.83,0:31:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那是什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.63,0:32:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}妨礙治安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Disorderly conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.94,0:32:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你信因果報應嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you believe in karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.38,0:32:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當然不信{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.05,0:32:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我信{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.25,0:32:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}至少今晚{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}At least tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.45,0:32:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}打電話給卡帝夫隊長{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Get Captain Cardiff on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.82,0:32:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們來處理米契的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let's do something about Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.99,0:32:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 什麼？  - 幫他保住飯碗{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-What?  -Get him his job back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他開槍了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He fired his weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.56,0:32:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他反應過度{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He overreacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.49,0:32:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在就打給卡帝夫{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Cardiff. On the phone. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.77,0:32:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}南茜，幫我接卡帝夫隊長{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Nancy, give me Captain Cardiff, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.77,0:32:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}反正也是等  不如做點有用的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We might as well do one  productive thing while we wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.64,0:32:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這對我只是舉手之勞  對他卻意義重大{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It requires very little of me  and will mean the world to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.08,0:32:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是非常便宜的投資{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's a very inexpensive investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.84,0:32:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我是道格史坦普{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hello, sir. This is Doug Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.11,0:32:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭斯安德沃想跟你談話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I have Francis Underwood for you.
